   -- where the nesting is the PARENT's content and terminates -- this one is a genuine cycle: every
   level renders another level, and Blazor does not terminate on it either.

   The pair exists so the fragment-scoped chain (Fragment.Composing) can be shown to distinguish the
   two cases rather than to weaken the guard. *@
